# Copy to app/.env.local (gitignored) and fill in. Testnet only.
#
# Secret of the VUSD faucet distributor account
# (GBBGQTNRGZ7BGNCUGNVBRSYUNBY2XCJ7UAAVYWA2OPMCWTQSGR3PPXGP). It is pre-funded
# with VUSD and only used to drip the asset to your fee account so you can test
# VUSD deposits. It is NOT the contract admin or the asset issuer, so a leak only
# risks the faucet's testnet VUSD balance.
#
# Retrieve it from your local stellar keystore:
#   echo "VITE_VUSD_FAUCET_SECRET=$(stellar keys show poof-faucet)" >> app/.env.local
VITE_VUSD_FAUCET_SECRET=

# Optional: durable indexer base URL (the Rust poof-indexer, e.g. on Railway).
# When set, the note scanner backfills commitment history that Soroban RPC has
# aged out of its ~7-day retention window. Unset → RPC-only (works until the
# contract is older than retention). No trailing slash.
#   VITE_INDEXER_URL=https://your-service.up.railway.app
VITE_INDEXER_URL=

# Optional: gasless-withdrawal relayer base URL (the poof-relayer service, e.g. on
# Railway/Fly). When set, Withdraw shows a "Gasless (via relayer)" toggle: a relayer
# submits + pays the Stellar network fee so the destination never needs XLM and no
# fee-payer links to you. Requires the fee-settling contract redeploy. No trailing
# slash. Unset → withdrawals self-submit exactly as before.
#   VITE_RELAYER_URL=https://your-relayer.up.railway.app
VITE_RELAYER_URL=
